Introspection utility for Ruby language.

Usage:
  <%= program %> [command] [options]
  <%= program %> help <command>
  <%= program %> -h | --help
  <%= program %> -v | --version

Commands:
<% commands.sort_by { |name, description| name }.each do |name, description| -%>
  <%= "%-16s" % name %>  <%= description %>
<% end -%>

Options:
  -h, --help        Show help.
      --version     Show application version end exit.
